{"tid":807251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★生吞白老鼠食蟲飲尿　貴州公司狠招懲罰不達標員工捱轟","createTime":"2018-09-05T11:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T11:31:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"15168c4a52da516ce81304a712bfd45964943421","tid":807251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:10:07.000Z","msg":"貴州六盤水市一間裝飾公司被揭發竟以淋水、生吞麵包蟲、白老鼠，甚至喝尿等方式懲罰業積不達標的員工，惹來輿論炮轟。<br />\n<br />\n該公司負責人事後重申，懲罰方式是員工自行提議，且最終亦只有實施淋水一項<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1829862/org/908a7bf932628959f7302d318c3a78ad.jpg/73Zrm19gNVXdQIboSZjW6Vw2D2bOCnKnc0xBBHNMQQQ?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1829862%2Forg%2F908a7bf932628959f7302d318c3a78ad.jpg%2F73Zrm19gNVXdQIboSZjW6Vw2D2bOCnKnc0xBBHNMQQQ%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=23484aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從網上片段所見，一名身穿西裝的「受害者」正站在一個大膠桶中，由另一名男子將一桶飲水機桶裝水從其頭上不停向下淋。據該公司其中一名李姓員工透露，淋水只是其中一種對不達標員工的懲罰，此外還有生吞麵包蟲、白老鼠，甚至要喝尿，「就當天我們定的懲罰有小老鼠、麵包蟲這些，當時我們這些沒有被懲罰的人都沒有看到，就留下那些被懲罰的人」。<br />\n<br />\n網上片段中亦可見到有一名員工示範生吞麵包蟲，以及有一杯裝滿黃色液體的疑似尿液。<br />\n<br />\n公司負責人陳先生事後接受內媒訪問時稱，單就淋水而言做法並不過火，「因為熱天各方面的話，我覺得淋淋水很正常」。但陳先生強調，喝尿並不衞生，生吞白老鼠則殘忍及有可能帶有細菌或病毒，故最終都沒有實施。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生又重申，上述的懲罰方式都是員工自行提議，並不是公司的意見，但公司會在日後的經營中杜絕不合理的處罰方式，更多從人文關懷等方面提升企業文化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/231801/%E9%87%8D%E5%8F%A3%E5%91%B3-%E7%94%9F%E5%90%9E%E7%99%BD%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0%E9%A3%9F%E8%9F%B2%E9%A3%B2%E5%B0%BF-%E8%B2%B4%E5%B7%9E%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%8B%A0%E6%8B%9B%E6%87%B2%E7%BD%B0%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%94%E6%A8%99%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%8D%B1%E8%BD%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F231801%2F%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%2591%25B3-%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2590%259E%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%25BC%25A0%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%259F%25B2%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E5%25B0%25BF-%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E5%25B7%259E%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E7%258B%25A0%25E6%258B%259B%25E6%2587%25B2%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%25A8%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%258D%25B1%25E8%25BD%259F&d=KIK8scGAc9EVp6u4k9Q9mf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=83f02935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/231801/%E9%87%8D%E5%8F%A3%E5%91%B3-%E7%94%9F%E5%90%9E%E7%99%BD%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0%E9%A3%9F%E8%9F%B2%E9%A3%B2%E5%B0%BF-%E8%B2%B4%E5%B7%9E%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%8B%A0%E6%8B%9B%E6%87%B2%E7%BD%B0%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%94%E6%A8%99%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%8D%B1%E8%BD%9F</a>"},{"pid":"630c7b3712c6d1b83baf7a3615bbdc9d42f34dcd","tid":807251,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1829871/org/eb2546a48cedc19ab91ebfa542ad4102.jpg/sd9DvYGi2aQqvhnM9edJEpEN_aNhP6eIccNku3HDZLs?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1829871%2Forg%2Feb2546a48cedc19ab91ebfa542ad4102.jpg%2Fsd9DvYGi2aQqvhnM9edJEpEN_aNhP6eIccNku3HDZLs%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=eec58371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公司負責人陳先生強調最終只有採用淋水作為懲罰方式。（影片截圖）"},{"pid":"f2fd53c3ec6fa75ca7f33a39be3e1784ce17eb11","tid":807251,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be75014f620f5c97c3942de538314103f96b49b","tid":807251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2fd53c3ec6fa75ca7f33a39be3e1784ce17eb11","tid":807251,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d814786f510dbbbc79a4cd67a154c28a42eb5c67","tid":807251,"uid":26752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"起來！願意做奴隸的人們！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 把我們的血肉，築成老闆新的長城！"},{"pid":"d2a5499183086664dc1d1659b447b2c806f38a64","tid":807251,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"不如食屎啦<br />\n<br />\n可能一試愛上"},{"pid":"401d7647667356b673749d1f4f9839486631eb1e","tid":807251,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/191338_041d93d80e5ea4e628aa2b31bb74f006.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F191338_041d93d80e5ea4e628aa2b31bb74f006.png&h=1a848703&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95f97ad1bd8656d794d7015c6a6559e459891575","tid":807251,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/191532_15640e93629b002be7b3dc48245ba355.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F191532_15640e93629b002be7b3dc48245ba355.png&h=c2b39d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f0969bc4cb03e6c0bd35a2fb97420993546901e","tid":807251,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:20:11.000Z","msg":"外國就冰桶挑戰，一去到大陸做即時cheap哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ea0eb20b8ddb812af73007d32106f55c92f444","tid":807251,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:28:39.000Z","msg":"仲返呢份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgm